text: Dominik Lechner (born 1 April 2005) is an Austrian professional footballer. He plays as a forward for 2. Liga club Liefering. ==Career== He started his career with the youth team of SV Kuchl. In 2012 he came to FC Red Bull Salzburg youth. From 2019 on he was in the Red Bull Salzburg Academy.Profil transfermarkt.at (German) In July 2022 he debuted for FC Liefering when he came on in the 65th minute for Zeteny Jano in the league match against Young Violets Austria Wien.Soccerway ==National team== Lechner played for the Austrian U 17 team.
